text: Phi Kappa may refer to: *Phi Kappa Literary Society, a debate society founded in 1820 at the University of Georgia *Phi Kappa (secondary), a secondary school fraternity founded in 1900 *Phi Kappa (Catholic fraternity), a higher education fraternity founded in 1889 and one of the two fraternities that merged to form Phi Kappa Theta
title: Phi Kappa
